OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777464668
OL,3,CDefendant jailed over 'grotesque
OL,4,Cobsession' with fishing nappies out of
OL,5,Cbins
OL,7,FA defendant who was spared jail after
OL,8,Fbeing assaulted while on remand is
OL,9,Fback in custody for returning to a
OL,10,F"grotesque obsession" of fishing
OL,11,Fsoiled nappies out of bins.
OL,13,FPrevious court hearings have been told
OL,14,Fthat Abbi Taylor, 47, who has also
OL,15,Fappeared on earlier court lists as
OL,16,FMartin Tarling, identifies as a woman,
OL,17,Fbut is being held at a men's prison.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
