PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777464668
OL,3,CDefendant jailed over 'grotesque
OL,4,Cobsession' with fishing nappies out of
OL,5,Cbins
OL,7,FNewcastle Crown Court heard that after
OL,8,Favoiding an immediate jail term in
OL,9,FAugust 2025 for a series of incidents
OL,10,Finvolving nappies being taken out of
OL,11,Fbins, Taylor returned to similar
OL,12,Fbehaviour within months.
OL,14,FTaylor was handed a criminal behaviour
OL,15,Forder by Nottinghamshire Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt in April 2023, that included a
OL,17,Fban on going within 10 metres of a
OL,18,Fnursery without a reasonable excuse.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777464668
OL,3,CDefendant jailed over 'grotesque
OL,4,Cobsession' with fishing nappies out of
OL,5,Cbins
OL,7,FDuring a sentencing hearing on Tuesday
OL,8,F(28 April) in Newcastle, Recorder Tony
OL,9,FHawks said: "The purpose of that order
OL,10,Fwas to tackle what is a grotesque
OL,11,Fobsession that you apparently have
OL,12,Fwith rooting around in bins near care
OL,13,Fhomes or nurseries in order to
OL,14,Fretrieve soiled nappies or
OL,15,Fincontinence wear."
OL,26,@qD@MOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777464668
OL,3,CDefendant jailed over 'grotesque
OL,4,Cobsession' with fishing nappies out of
OL,5,Cbins
OL,7,FIn August 2025, Taylor was given a
OL,8,Fsuspended prison sentence after
OL,9,Fpleading guilty to offences including
OL,10,Fbreaching that order with a series of
OL,11,Fincidents at nurseries in South
OL,12,FTyneside.
OL,14,FThese included staff at a nursery in
OL,15,FCleadon noticing nappies "much larger
OL,16,Fthan the ones they used" being dumped
OL,17,Fon the premises "on a fortnightly
OL,18,Fbasis", and the manager at another
OL,19,FSouth Shields nursery seeing someone
OL,20,F"rooting around inside" one of the
OL,21,Fclinical waste bins.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@XO]yD@QOUzD@FO]|D@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777464668
OL,3,CDefendant jailed over 'grotesque
OL,4,Cobsession' with fishing nappies out of
OL,5,Cbins
OL,7,FTaylor was spared an immediate jail
OL,8,Fterm on that occasion after the judge
OL,9,Fheard she "had had a particularly
OL,10,Fdifficult time in custody" and "been
OL,11,Fsubject to a number of physical
OL,12,Fassaults".
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, Taylor, of South Shields,
OL,15,Fwas jailed for 30 months after
OL,16,Fadmitting to four breaches of a
OL,17,Fcriminal behaviour order with four
OL,18,Fseparate incidents in December last
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@ZO]rD@`OUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777464668
OL,3,CDefendant jailed over 'grotesque
OL,4,Cobsession' with fishing nappies out of
OL,5,Cbins
OL,7,FThese included soiled nappies being
OL,8,Ftaken from a bin and left strewn in a
OL,9,Fgarden.
OL,11,FMr Hawks told Taylor: "It is the view
OL,12,Fof the psychiatrist who has examined
OL,13,Fyou, you are not motivated by any
OL,14,Fsexual motive.
OL,16,F"I am prepared to accept that, however
OL,17,Fyour conduct is highly antisocial and
OL,18,Fextremely distressing to people who
OL,19,Fare affected by it.
OL,26,@sD@WOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777464668
OL,3,CDefendant jailed over 'grotesque
OL,4,Cobsession' with fishing nappies out of
OL,5,Cbins
OL,7,F"You have got to understand when you
OL,8,Fare released, if you continue to
OL,9,Fbehave in this way, you will receive
OL,10,Flonger and longer periods of
OL,11,Fimprisonment."
OL,13,FHe said the latest incidents were
OL,14,F"grotesque, grossly antisocial and no
OL,15,Fdoubt caused considerable distress to
OL,16,Fpeople to have witnessed or are
OL,17,Faffected by your behaviour".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]vD@AOUyD@[O]
